      • setResourceInfo

        public final void setResourceInfo(WMSLayer.ResourceInfo resourceInfo)
        Parameters:
        resourceInfo - - An optional resource info object. The default behavior of a WMSLayer is to execute a WMS GetCapabilities request, which requires using a proxy page. If resourceInfo is specified a GetCapabilities request is not executed and no proxy page is required.

      • setTransparent

      • setVisibleLayers

        public final void setVisibleLayers(java.lang.String[] visibleLayers)
        Parameters:
        visibleLayers - - A list of layer names that represent the layers to include in the exported map. By default no layers are visible. The order of layers in the list defines the order the layers will display in the map.
